{"version":3,"term":{"cols":80,"rows":24},"timestamp":1778303643,"command":"bash deploy/demo/screencast.sh","env":{"SHELL":"/bin/zsh"}}
[0.037, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J"]
[0.011, "o", "============================================================\r\nSpendGuard — Agent Runtime Spend Guardrails\r\nPhase 3 Wedge: Contract DSL hot-path evaluator (POC)\r\n\r\n  agent step → sidecar (<5ms) → reads contract.yaml → STOP / DEGRADE / pass\r\n                                                    → audit row durable\r\n                                                    → ledger reservation atomic\r\n============================================================\r\n"]
[3.009, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== 1. The contract a customer ships (excerpt from bundle) ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.015, "o", "\u001b[2m# Declarative when/then; POC subset of Contract DSL §6/§7.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.030, "o", "  apiVersion: contract.spendguard.io/v1alpha1\r\n  kind: Contract\r\n  metadata:\r\n    id: $CONTRACT_LOGICAL_ID\r\n    name: demo-contract\r\n  spec:\r\n    budgets:\r\n      - id: $DEMO_BUDGET_ID\r\n        limit_amount_atomic: \"1000000000\"\r\n        currency: USD\r\n        reservation_ttl_seconds: 600\r\n        require_hard_cap: true\r\n    rules:\r\n      - id: hard-cap-deny\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        when:\r\n          budget_id: $DEMO_BUDGET_ID\r\n          claim_amount_atomic_gt: \"1000000000\"\r\n        then:\r\n          decision: STOP\r\n"]
[4.132, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== 2. Send a $2000 claim — twice the $1000 hard cap ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.181, "o", "\u001b[2m# Adapter raises DecisionStopped before any reservation is taken.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.491, "o", "[demo] connecting to sidecar at /var/run/spendguard/adapter.sock\r\n[demo] handshake ok session_id=019e0b28-88fd-7d23-aa5d-2302d034b6d1\r\n[demo] DENY raised decision_id=019e0b28-8900-7243-be4c-dcf28f2a8de3 reason_codes=['BUDGET_EXHAUSTED'] matched_rule_ids=['33333333-3333-4333-8333-333333333333:44444444-4444-4444-8444-444444444444:hard-cap-deny'] audit_decision_event_id=019e0b28-8900-7243-be4c-dd0d6fa0c8a9\r\n[demo] DENY assertions PASS\r\n"]
[3.009, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== 3. The audit chain — ledger.audit_outbox ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.012, "o", "\u001b[2m# Carrier ledger_transactions row (no entries) + 1 audit_outbox row.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.297, "o", " operation_kind  | posting_state |             decision_id              \r\n-----------------+---------------+--------------------------------------\r\n denied_decision | posted        | 019e0b28-8900-7243-be4c-dcf28f2a8de3\r\n(1 row)\r\n\r\n"]
[2.027, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== 4. ... and what canonical_events received (compliance store) ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.017, "o", "\u001b[2m# Outbox forwarder pushed the audit row immutably.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.170, "o", "        event_type         |            source             \r\n---------------------------+-------------------------------\r\n spendguard.audit.decision | sidecar://demo/sidecar-demo-1\r\n spendguard.audit.decision | sidecar://demo/sidecar-demo-1\r\n spendguard.audit.decision | sidecar://demo/sidecar-demo-1\r\n(3 rows)\r\n\r\n"]
[3.025, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== 5. The wedge in one diagram ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.023, "o", "\r\n  agent  ─►  sidecar  ─►  ledger  ─►  audit_outbox  ─►  canonical_events\r\n              │             │             │\r\n              │             │             └─ Postgres SERIALIZABLE\r\n              │             └─ atomic reserve / denied_decision\r\n              └─ contract evaluator (Stage 2, <5 ms hot-path)\r\n\r\n  Demo modes (all green): decision · invoice · agent · release · ttl_sweep · deny\r\n"]
[4.108, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32mPhase 3 wedge — Predict ∩ Control intersection.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mhttps://github.com/m24927605/agentic-flow-cost-evaluation/pull/1\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
